822
02:03:11,167 --> 02:03:17,207
<i>Open the door this moment,
like revealing hidden secrets</i>

823
02:03:17,333 --> 02:03:23,374
<i>The joy of holding ones hand,
the suffering of losing one.</i>

824
02:03:23,500 --> 02:03:29,874
<i>Can't hold myself from picturing,
like the spinning globe</i>

